s, but the same Lord.","year":59},{"id":"recc9Zz9RyKamQ42U","ref":"1Cor.12.6","text":"And there are diversities of operations, but it is the same God which worketh all in all.","year":59},{"id":"recldESHdMagdIIzN","ref":"1Cor.12.7","text":"But the manifestation of the Spirit is given to every man to profit withal.","year":59},{"id":"recqatcdc2IPJ7aPP","ref":"1Cor.12.8","text":"For to one is given by the Spirit the word of wisdom; to another the word of knowledge by the same Spirit;","year":59}]}
